{"tid":1362503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現在不管做什麼行動，總有一群人，不停向你叫嗌「中計！中計！」、「別中計，快撤！」、「小心陷阱，別中計」。","createTime":"2019-07-25T01:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T08:15:46.000Z","uid":107060,"like":77,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6a502886a38d4c8d21be126ddc9bed00e7b057","tid":1362503,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"現在不管做什麼行動，總有一群人，不停向你叫嗌「中計！中計！」、「別中計，快撤！」、「小心陷阱，別中計」。<br />\n一時間，遍地計策，漫山陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n你回想一下：<br />\n1,一個政府，連行會成員都管唔住。<br />\n2,一個特首，會畀建制議員用粗口問候。<br />\n3,一個警務署署長，講句英文都Can't find the right word。<br />\n4,安排做公關SHOW，不斷道歉，但每次結果都係得罪更多人。<br />\n5,721本來安排好曬，準備好譴責抗爭者毁國徽、掟磚、放火。結果警黑自己友同晚元朗搞恐襲，搞到唔知譴責邊個好。<br />\n6,出人出錢搞撐警集會，建制人士貪口爽叫人用籐條打仔，結果搞到要自己辭職走人。<br />\n7,好威咁吹雞打人，然後影大合照方便大家起底。<br />\n<br />\n你面對呢班「冇撚曬計」嘅人，你驚「中計」？<br />\n<br />\n或者唔講咁長篇，下次再有人話你中計，你貼返呢個「噴胡椒噴到自己集體跣底」嘅GIF畀佢睇，難道這也是苦肉計？城府真係咁深？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/S6wdvjzjsuwOAPG2eM/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FS6wdvjzjsuwOAPG2eM%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a74af634&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52a10e5271b144562c312f148f895c227ca01f34","tid":1362503,"uid":107060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8518aa2d38d84080fe33490a3a612a37ab9c071","tid":1362503,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dbb94ef0454de956a411926a20c9cffceb837c","tid":1362503,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4db131cc0156254b5f0b3f0c724630bfa4350a","tid":1362503,"uid":107060,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:43:43.000Z","m